#### 1.4 Fix ESC Key Priority (30 min)
**File:** `src/hooks/useEscapeKey.ts` (Line 31)

**Current Code:**
```typescript
if (priority >= currentPriority) {  // ❌ Equal priority conflicts
```

**Fix:**
```typescript
if (priority > currentPriority) {   // ✅ Only strictly higher priority wins
```

**Reasoning:** The `>=` allows equal priority handlers to both execute if they register in the right order. Changing to `>` ensures ONLY strictly higher priority wins.

---

#### 1.5 Fix Modal Responsive Sizing (30 min)
**File:** `src/components/Modal.tsx` (Line 56)

**Current Code:**
```typescript
className={`... max-w-[90vw] w-full`}  // ❌ 90% width even on desktop
```

**Fix:**
```typescript
className={`... w-full max-w-[90vw] sm:max-w-2xl`}  // ✅ Responsive breakpoints
```

**Result:**
- Mobile (< 640px): 90% viewport width
- Tablet/Desktop (640px+): Max 672px (2xl)

