## Design Considerations

### Spacing System
**Tokens:**
- `widget-padding`: 16px (p-4)
- `content-gap`: 16px (space-y-4)
- `button-gap`: 8px (gap-2)
- `grid-gap`: 24px (gap-6)
- `section-margin`: 24px (mb-6)
- `section-margin-lg`: 32px (mb-8)

**Usage:**
- Widget internal padding: Always `p-4`
- Content vertical spacing: Always `space-y-4`
- Button groups: Always `gap-2`
- Widget grid: Always `gap-6`

### Widget Standards
**Button Sizing:** `w-full px-4 py-2 rounded-lg` (uniform 40px height)
**Content Spacing:** `space-y-4` between sections, `space-y-3` between list items
**Colors:** Use accent colors for distinct widgets (blue/magenta/cyan)
**Drag Handle:** Upper-right corner, `right-2 top-2`

### Modal Sizing
**Responsive Breakpoints:**
- Mobile (< 640px): `max-w-[90vw]` (90% width)
- Tablet/Desktop (640px+): `max-w-2xl` (672px)

**Content Padding:** Always `p-4` (16px)

### Performance
**Bundle Size Impact:**
- New AboutModal: ~2KB
- Tailwind config: 0KB (compile-time only)
- Widget rebuilds: 0KB (same components, just refactored)
- **Expected:** No significant bundle increase

